imdb.plot outline: Tim Knight kicks off the show with a look at how the charts view the day's market. Then Tom Sosnoff and Tony Battista jump in and don't waste a minute. They talk about the best way to end the day and where they see the seams of opportunity for tomorrow. They talk fast because they know you think quick. If you can only make one call, make it "Last Call."
